pageContext.claim: “[CNN and MSNBC's ratings] dropped to a level that nobody could believe because now that they see the Mueller report, where you look at their finding -- I mean, the finding was very, very strong.”
pageContext.analysis: Nielsen ratings for March 2019 have yet to be released. While Fox held on to it's number one spot in February, Hannity and Maddow were neck and neck for viewers depending on how the numbers were calculated.
